{"tid":2145679,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"證監會︰密切注視制裁對本港金融穩定可帶來的影響","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:18:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b3a669eff45fe4244ad47749b00d8a84353929","tid":2145679,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542561-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542561-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDOvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=5babfe85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542561-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a821b312\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542561-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國宣布制裁11名香港與內地官員及前官員，包括特首林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n證監會發表聲明，表示正密切注視制裁措施對中介人的運作、投資者的利益，以及香港金融市場的穩定和秩序可能帶來的影響。<br />\n<br />\n證監會呼籲，中介人考慮相關制裁的影響時，應謹慎評估可能面對的任何法律、業務及商業風險，證監會期望任何應對制裁的措施，都具備必要性和秉持公平的原則，並以維護客戶最佳利益及確保市場廉潔穩健為依歸。"}]}